main event: A witness observed an unidentified object in the sky over Torrence, California on March 6, 1967.
interesting points: The sighting occurred at 11:48 p.m. and lasted for approximately 2-3 minutes., The object was dark in color and irregular in shape., The witness was unable to provide further details about the object., The case number for the report is 1967-03-6979384., The document is part of a report from the Foreign Technology Division, AFSC.
witness description: a person who observed the sighting
